name: ISET
overview:
Located in the heart of Louisville Kentucky; ISET is a Veteran owned and family operated. We know what it means to develop partnerships with our customers and work together for many years to come. It is our goal to provide small and medium sized company’s with everything they need when it comes to Voice & Data.

ISET’s management team has over 15 years of experience and unparalleled expertise in the assessment and implementation of NEC voice platforms and can provide solutions for telephone systems, voice mail, data applications, (LAN, WAN), video conferencing, fast internet access, long distance service, local dial tone, document systems, and wireless applications.

Our dedicated management team strives to enable organizations to meet their strategic objectives through best-of-breed data and voice applications and solutions. Combined with a daily relentless passion and commitment to serve our customers. Like our customers, ISET’s management team values quality of service above all else. Ongoing training in design, installation, quality assurance, safety and customer support ensures that we retain that level of excellence.
